----------------------------------------------------------------------

The generated HTML report (security-template.html) loads Chart.js from a
public CDN at view time, for rendering the risk-distribution doughnut chart.

  Chart.js — MIT License — https://www.chartjs.org/
  Copyright (c) 2014-2024 Chart.js Contributors

Chart.js is not bundled in this distribution; it is referenced via CDN with
an SRI integrity hash and degrades gracefully to an inline SVG chart when
offline. No other third-party code is included.
